# Role-based access control for the Full Toolkit member pages.
# Requires Netlify Identity to be enabled, and the "full-toolkit" role to be
# granted via netlify/functions/stripe-webhook.js after a successful payment.
#
# Anyone whose Netlify Identity JWT includes the "full-toolkit" role is served
# the page as normal. Everyone else (including logged-out visitors) is sent to
# pricing.html instead. This is enforced at Netlify's CDN edge, not in the
# browser, so it can't be bypassed by disabling JavaScript.
#
# PAYWALL CURRENTLY DISABLED (temporary — growth phase):
# All /member-* pages are open to everyone, logged in or not. To bring the
# paywall back later, delete the pass-through line below and uncomment the
# two Role=full-toolkit lines.
#
# /member-*  /member-:splat  200!  Role=full-toolkit
# /member-*  /pricing.html   401!
/member-*  /member-:splat  200!
